{
  "title": "Roasted Ground Clove Indian Udupi Dal",
  "description": "A buttery, crisp Indian Udupi dish perfect for post-workout or a quick weeknight meal featuring ground clove and a deglaze technique. Serve in a molcajete for a touch of rustic authenticity.",
  "cuisine": "Indian",
  "diet": null,
